# Financial Risk Credit Credit Exposures OREO Impairment Amount

## identifier
de7849

## status
Standard

## type
undefined

## definition
This is the value of the provision for impairment in relation to all real estate acquired by the reporting party in full or partial settlement of a loan or similar facility through enforcement of security arrangements. This category excludes  property controlled under 'mortgagee in possession' rights.

## guidance
undefined

